This button allows to resize any image loaded into the browser from the page context menu. It is based on a Firefox addon that I used to use ([url=https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/image2icon]Image2Icon[/url]) that has not been updated for three years and it doesn't work on Firefox multi-process.

