[size=150][b]Features[/b][/size]
The options for this button can be accessed by Left clicking on it.
[list]
[*] All tasks added by this button are performed from the page context menu.
[*] Possibility to resize an image to a fixed size or to a percentage of the original image size.
[*] Possibility to convert an image to Base64 without resizing it.
[*] The list of sizes in the context menu can be edited to add your own sizes and/or remove the sizes that you don't need/want.
[*] Possibility to view the current site`s favicon from the [b]View current site`s favicon[/b] item on the context menu.[/list]

